data.meta_description: Tony Parked Reported to Have Had Affair With Teammate's Wife - San Antonio Spurs' star Tony Parker's marriage with Eva Longoria ended in 2010 amidst reports that Parker (right) cheated on her with teammate Brent Barry's wife. The latter marriage ended as well. Technical foul...Â nah, straight up flagrant.(Photos from Left: Ronald Martinez/Getty Images, Al Bello/Getty Images) - Some of these stories were way out of bounds.
